    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i don't know if \"carving out a space\" is even possible when the fatigue is this deep. sometimes i just look at everything and think... what if the only way to actually stop the noise and the effort is to just not be here anymore? it feels like the only way to truly rest.",
